    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an uncompromising specimen of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom-ready condition, having been curated to the highest standards of mechanical and aesthetic perfection. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the meticulously preserved interior, reflects a history of fastidious ownership. This is an investment-grade opportunity for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than the absolute pinnacle of quality.",
