    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m so excited for whoever gets to drive this beauty home. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and it\u2019s in such incredible shape\u2014it practically looks and smells like it just left the showroom! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a gem that\u2019s been pampered its whole life, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
