      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it still looks and feels brand new! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. I'm looking for a quick sale, so I've priced it to be a total steal for anyone looking for top-tier quality. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
