      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a fully overhauled dual-VANOS system. This chassis has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and documented rod bearing replacement. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivers tactile shifts through a precise gate, feeding power to a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its original geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the hydraulic steering rack provides the unfiltered feedback quintessential to this analog masterpiece. Paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior demonstrates zero bolster wear or pixel degradation. A mechanically superlative example for the discerning collector.",
